  "description": "bodyFreq=55Hz (A1 — the permanent habitat). Even harmonic stack: ÷2 (A0 octave below), ÷4 (A-1), ÷6 (subharmonic fifth). All even dividers per OWL-III — no alien content, pure harmonic layering. bodyLevel 0.4: MIDI voice is primary, the body enriches. The cleanest Owlfish foundation: a major triad built downward from A.",
